{"tid":1790123,"cid":18,"subCid":0,"title":"一個可能好多香港人都唔識既冷知識啱啱比我發現左","createTime":"2019-12-19T18:02:28.000Z","updateTime":"2019-12-19T22:34:19.000Z","uid":92376,"like":3,"dislike":8,"uniUserReply":11,"replies":[{"pid":"52834f62858bb158090818b9c62a961e1c933a39","tid":1790123,"uid":92376,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-12-19T18:02:28.000Z","msg":"有無留意到<br />\n全世界有咁多種語言<br />\n唯獨係我地用中文字既地區<br />\n先會出現廣東話 普通話 客家話 台山話 閔南話 上海話 四川話<br />\n但從來無人會叫其他語言做乜話<br />\n例如無人會講日話 韓話 英話 法話 德話 意話 越話 泰話 俄話<br />\n我諗左好耐 終於發現原"},{"pid":"293687d8b4a61e0ffdaeba029e2b6ec888bb973c","tid":1790123,"uid":38904,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-12-19T18:03:51.000Z","msg":"巧叻叻<img src=\"/assets/faces/pigxm/clap.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"5226ef5929821aedfc5e087ddd25eb86100b3ac1","tid":1790123,"uid":161208,"like":2,"dislike":0,"score":2,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-12-19T18:07:58.000Z","msg":"會叫 粵語"},{"pid":"d7529add354ddd910d9d663d4a9f8230d8b8b9c9","tid":1790123,"uid":204480,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-12-19T18:10:01.000Z","msg":"啲冷知識掂完習總隻手變曬熱知識<img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2xm/jable.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2xm/jable.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2xm/bomb.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2xm/bomb.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"5600a638884787cc227b65b5b6e5029b96d59be7","tid":1790123,"uid":136186,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"5226ef5929821aedfc5e087ddd25eb86100b3ac1","tid":1790123,"uid":161208,"like":2,"dislike":0,"score":2,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-12-19T18:07:58.000Z","msg":"會叫 粵語"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-12-19T18:11:25.000Z","msg":"正"},{"pid":"86c426c460ce6a061c3f3028a2fc41f6f4ac79aa","tid":1790123,"uid":34343,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-12-19T18:11:41.000Z","msg":"西班牙話 葡萄牙話<img src=\"/assets/faces/dogxm/touch.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"7583d2eab98e491f4d